div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QlZTMZ5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0V3s4PB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YhxdmFn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qYRqHc9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FSTDkAe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Gertie tax</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zXN9Awb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Baby Bruce tax</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JdSTEQM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nessie tax</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2kfvROG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[danat101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Its not that complicated</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0tEbHzt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pYPOnBW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0tEbHzt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[chukyrlaw]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>French Fry Fashion</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yiHWBBx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/76kBpSz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A significant portion of my wardrobe probably falls into McDonald's corporate branding guidelines, which is honestly one of my many life goals</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EIrhVRL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of the first times I donned my french fry earrings was for a local news segment in Chicago a few years ago. Morning news appearances require me to get up at 4am (a time I would be much more likely to go to bed) but they are fun nonetheless!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q02RDpO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Earring closeup! I love their smiles :)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ofo5u7t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Not sure if anyone was ever curious about how I compile these photos, but here's one of the images I used before cutting it out of the background. I was originally just gonna share the photos straight outta my phone but being me, I had to go and complicate the process just for the sake of the tedium (for which I am most certainly a glutton). I made all kinds of minute changes to this image before adding it to the final compilation. I updated clothing colors and even extended my legs. Photoshop is pretty solid at background removal, but I always have to go in manually to clean it up so I often just do it all myself anyways.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/chSC66z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This photo didn't make the cut but I figured I'd share it anyways. Fun fact: the Etch A Sketch in my hand is my red FAO Schwarz swarovski crystal edition, for which only four were ever made in the world. Color me cheeky!

Hope you all had a good weekend!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yiHWBBx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[pikajane]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing but net</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dKqaGRQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gyi9Z4c.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/dKqaGRQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheDiscoVampire]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Professional at work</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VuZHDVi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gyRMS1e.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>must be drugs dealer in disguise or double job in this economy. Lol joke guys!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VuZHDVi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheWhatever666]]></dc:creator></item><item><title></title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ppZ83ap</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ryv69go.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ppZ83ap</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rainbowcrab95772]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Truth</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/s2B60En</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H0yzLte.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/s2B60En</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[clemdarkstarzero]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Red Sonja – art nouveau style</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XKQwDeC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KsneUri.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A commission painted by french artist fred.ian</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rh9L8hN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; heigh